  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Mini invasive spine surgery is very common since a few time. Posterior arthrodesis
      associated to libération have good functional résults and presents a very little
      complication cases.

      So that's why St Joseph Hospital spine surgeon made thé hypothesis that This kind os surgery
      can be associated to fast track surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
